{"tid":790462,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"summer lesson PSVR《夏日課程：艾莉森與新城千里》","createTime":"2018-08-23T04:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T17:05:41.000Z","uid":170473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b3fc5b01b58de1a31edba35db2a55d17af9d325e","tid":790462,"uid":170473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:28:47.000Z","msg":"《夏日課程：艾莉森與新城千里》繁中版 8 月 23 日發售 豪華首批特典情報同步公開<br />\n（GNN 記者 KEN 報導） 2018-07-20 17:59:15<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/122332_d7d3db378c24319c84526702164a68ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F122332_d7d3db378c24319c84526702164a68ab.jpg&h=b59a13dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　台灣萬代南夢宮娛樂今（20）日宣布，將在 2018 年 8 月 23 日推出繁體中文版遊戲 PS VR《夏日課程：艾莉森與新城千里》，並公開首批特典內容。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n「她，真的近在眼前」<br />\n <br />\n　　本作完整收錄好評發布中的《夏日課程 艾莉森・史諾》以及《夏日課程 新城千里》，玩家於本作中可和溫柔沈穩的「艾莉森」以及強勢任性的大小姐「新城千里」，兩位性格截然不同的女主角展開邂逅與交流，享受共同度過的夏日時光、體驗透過 PSVR 遊玩所帶來身歷其境的樂趣。<br />\n <br />\n「艾莉森・史諾篇」遊戲特色<br />\n <br />\n　　與艾莉森共度 7 日的舞台，是在晴朗的夏日晴空與海洋之下，拓展於庭院裡的大自然與老民房的緣廊，邀您共享暑假輕旅行的閒適氣氛。隨著與溫柔地向您噓寒問暖的她相處，您將忘卻繁忙的日常&hellip;&hellip; 這是一個以「療癒」為主題的 VR 體驗內容系列。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/122408_3e26cd33266bf27e30f30558f67263ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F122408_3e26cd33266bf27e30f30558f67263ef.jpg&h=e93c2a13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/122417_652c7b4d8faacc7d9522b7885f540cf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F122417_652c7b4d8faacc7d9522b7885f540cf7.jpg&h=765fc31e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n「新城千里篇」遊戲特色<br />\n <br />\n　　您被指定擔任住在郊區的名門千金「新城千里」的家庭教師，將在 7 天內教導學生現代社會的流行與常識，包括電腦的使用方式或享受漫畫與電玩的樂趣。<br />\n <br />\n　　然而個性古靈精怪的她，總是用「老師可是我出錢雇用來的」當藉口，將您捲進千奇百怪的任性要求中。<br />\n <br />\n　　本篇的目的在於「深入追求 VR 體驗的可能性」。個性強勢又最愛見到老師慌慌張張的模樣&hellip;&hellip; 隨著與這樣前所未見的特殊學生相處，老實配合她的要求，您將經歷發揮 VR 特性的驚奇體驗與不可思議的感受。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/122433_bed67b2a104fc099c3ea32ae036d7641.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F122433_bed67b2a104fc099c3ea32ae036d7641.jpg&h=8a2d6f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/122721_4490253081759d7f328713a57f10a555.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F122721_4490253081759d7f328713a57f10a555.jpg&h=df9efe19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n首批特典內容<br />\n <br />\n　　凡購買《夏日課程：艾莉森與新城千里》繁體中文版的玩家將可獲得以下數位特典內容：<br />\n <br />\n4 款遊戲內服飾下載代碼：含「歌德搖滾」、「kawaii 薄荷」（艾莉森・史諾篇）、「薄暮色罩衫」、「黑刺繡罩衫」（新城千里篇）。<br />\n3 款夏日專屬泳裝服飾下載代碼：含「比基尼 乳石英」（艾莉森・史諾篇）、「比基尼 螢石」（新城千里篇）、「比基尼 藍色托帕石」（宮本光篇）。<br />\n2 款 PlayStation 4 可動主題：艾莉森與千里大小姐 Q 版娃趴趴走。<br />\n <br />\n　　此外，凡購買繁體中文實體版的玩家，可另獲得台灣香港地區限定特典「夏日課程：艾莉森與新城千里 特製吊飾」，讓兩位可愛的女主角長伴玩家左右。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/122521_787968fa65dac547be0705843cbe633f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F122521_787968fa65dac547be0705843cbe633f.jpg&h=5642eddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n※ 欲使用「宮本光服裝：比基尼 藍色托帕石」，需擁有《夏日課程：宮本光》遊戲軟體。<br />\n※ 示意圖僅供參考，請以實際物品為準。<br />\n※ 內容、樣式可能未經告知有部分變更。<br />\n※ 數量有限，詳細請洽購買店家。<br />\n <br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/122535_f6a27841585a6f80e284848f65bc5ff1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F122535_f6a27841585a6f80e284848f65bc5ff1.jpg&h=20455567&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「歌德搖滾」（艾莉森・史諾篇）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/122545_1399e5a106a21c4707535cc7cfdf8165.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F122545_1399e5a106a21c4707535cc7cfdf8165.jpg&h=021cd50d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n「kawaii 薄荷」（艾莉森・史諾篇）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/122556_b33097e7c6b805d989c1e5d28a6b90d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F122556_b33097e7c6b805d989c1e5d28a6b90d7.jpg&h=e181fdd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n「薄暮色罩衫」（新城千里篇）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/122610_8df5313c429bf3ed8ceb10da9e4139a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F122610_8df5313c429bf3ed8ceb10da9e4139a9.jpg&h=3fca0c6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n「黑刺繡罩衫」（新城千里篇）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/122622_4d2dc340637ad7b8e24be8c1e79fe7ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F122622_4d2dc340637ad7b8e24be8c1e79fe7ac.jpg&h=2316c849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\nPlayStation 4 可動主題（艾莉森・史諾篇）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/122634_886af386645ab567c887aff02b53aabf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F122634_886af386645ab567c887aff02b53aabf.jpg&h=aee4ba8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\nPlayStation 4 可動主題（新城千里篇）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=66PhX349veA&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D66PhX349veA%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=h7c0o%2BmwdMUlfomTdpq4wTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=d2c0c6db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=66PhX349veA&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"c57010f00019e5737d6b2b3e0e7b5611f574de66","tid":790462,"uid":170473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:30:55.000Z","msg":"多唔多人有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8a932d9d7f4d797b2d0c78afa7259d37f2fdb6","tid":790462,"uid":3109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:32:16.000Z","msg":"出左未實體版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"5b635e2066a3f98509db374358352d6fbc11d129","tid":790462,"uid":170473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec8a932d9d7f4d797b2d0c78afa7259d37f2fdb6","tid":790462,"uid":3109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:32:16.000Z","msg":"出左未實體版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:37:09.000Z","msg":"出了 送匙扣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddef9c7162bc6b3608c56d5d21ef07edbd3016a1","tid":790462,"uid":3109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5b635e2066a3f98509db374358352d6fbc11d129","tid":790462,"uid":170473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec8a932d9d7f4d797b2d0c78afa7259d37f2fdb6","tid":790462,"uid":3109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:32:16.000Z","msg":"出左未實體版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:37:09.000Z","msg":"出了 送匙扣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:40:38.000Z","msg":"出mk睇睇先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5248a8a5c0bcffa441cc832cff3fbf95bb1d3cff","tid":790462,"uid":170473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:11:28.0